<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#evidence220">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Evidence"/>
  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Security The Smithsonian takes reasonable steps to design and manage our Websites technology to ensure that its information technology systems applications and information technology infrastructure are secure The Smithsonian requires credit card processing be secured based on compliance with Payment Card Industry PCI standards When you use your credit card for any purchase on a Smithsonian Website that transaction is always encrypted when traveling over the Internet</evidenceContent>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

